		<RichText x="738" y="223" fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff" width="423" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">场上无雷萤存在时，雷萤术士使用雾虚草灯召唤3只雷萤。</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="739" y="479" width="407" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">雷萤术士使用雾虚草灯命令雷萤突进，造成<span color="#ffacff">20%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="739" y="735" width="437" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">雷萤术士杀死召唤的雷萤，缓慢升空并附属<span textDecoration="underline">特斯拉线圈</span><span>同时产生爆炸，造成</span><span color="#df99ff">100%</span><span>伤害，并以较快的速度移动，向玩家进行高频电击持续造成</span><span color="#df99ff">25%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1411" y="223" width="423" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">雷萤术士召唤的雷萤间歇性的向玩家喷吐雷球，造成<span color="#ffacff">20%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="479" width="439" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">雷萤术士使用雾虚草灯唤出1道落雷，造成<span color="#ffacff">100%</span><span>伤害，落雷留下雷痕地面，接触持续造成</span><span color="#ffacff">25%</span><span>伤害。<br/></span><span color="#f94ccb">攻击强化：</span><span>召唤至多6道的落雷。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="735" fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff" width="439" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">距离玩家较远时，雷萤术士进行连续4段的传送；距离玩家太近时，传送至玩家后方。</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
