		<RichText x="66" y="1008" width="438" height="39" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">特斯拉线圈：<span color="#ffacff">8雷</span><span>盾，持续15s后自动击破。该状态下，抗打断0，免疫风场力。</span></p>
